			<p><strong>Print Method:</strong> Premium Direct-to-Garment (DTG) printing for realistic, vintage, lasting designs.</p>
			<p><strong>Style &amp; Fit:</strong> Relaxed oversized fit featuring a unique vintage &quot;snowflake&quot; wash that looks even better wash after wash.</p>
			<p><strong>Origin:</strong> Proudly Made in the USA.</p>
		{%- when 'tanktop' -%}
			<p><strong>Base Item:</strong> Gildan 2200.</p>
			<p><strong>Sizes:</strong> S to 3XL (True to size).</p>
			<p><strong>Colors:</strong> Select via color swatches</p>
			<p><strong>Print Method:</strong> Premium Direct-to-Garment (DTG) printing for realistic, vintage, lasting designs.</p>
			<p><strong>Style &amp; Fit:</strong> Classic fit that perfectly balances relaxed comfort with a flattering silhouette for all body types.</p>
			<p><strong>Material:</strong> Premium 100% American-grown cotton (Heavyweight 6 oz/yd&sup2;, 18 Singles).</p>
			<p><strong>Versatility:</strong> Highly breathable and comfortable</p>
			<p><strong>Origin:</strong> Proudly Made in the USA.</p>
		{%- when 'comfort-1717' -%}
			<p><strong>Base Item:</strong> Comfort Colors 1717.</p>
			<p><strong>Sizes:</strong> S to 4XL.</p>
			<p><strong>Colors:</strong> Select via color swatches</p>
			<p><strong>Material:</strong> 100% Ring Spun US Cotton.</p>
			<p><strong>Style &amp; Fit:</strong> Relaxed unisex fit, casual style.</p>
			<p><strong>Print Method:</strong> Premium Direct-to-Garment (DTG) printing for realistic, vintage, lasting designs.</p>
			<p><strong>Premium Quality:</strong> Made from 100% Ring Spun US Cotton (6.1 oz/yd&sup2;) for a superior, heavyweight feel.</p>
			<p><strong>Origin:</strong> Proudly Made in the USA.</p>
		{%- when 'hoodie' -%}
			<p><strong>Base Item:</strong> Gildan 18500.</p>
			<p><strong>Sizes:</strong> S to 5XL.</p>
